    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281100/extras/7e299269729f3ee3b7501147cd0dee31.avif?t=1754938007\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281100/extras_big/7e299269729f3ee3b7501147cd0dee31.avif?t=1754938007 width=800 height=295 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跳线乔恩 (Jumper Jon) 是一款 30 秒银河恶魔城风格的平台冒险游戏！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >琼恩是一个生活在地狱边缘的小恶魔。有一天，有东西从上面掉下来，造成了巨大的冲击。乔恩决定一探究竟，发现那是一个名叫简的女孩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们将一起发现地球上善恶失衡的根源并与之抗争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281100/extras/ebff8a06760c12fa464a981858550b1c.poster.avif?t=1754938007\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281100/extras/ebff8a06760c12fa464a981858550b1c.webm?t=1754938007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281100/extras/ebff8a06760c12fa464a981858550b1c.mp4?t=1754938007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用 30 秒的时间探索地狱！无论你的时间用完还是死亡，你都会回来并保留你得到的物品！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >类银河战士恶魔城风格的冒险，具有独特的游戏概念！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现一个引人入胜且很酷的故事！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找特殊物品和能力并探索地狱！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救灵魂以获得收藏奖杯！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单直观的游戏控制！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漂亮的卡通风格图形！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人惊叹的原声带！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281100/extras/b94319be73f31af6ddc610d53cb2d484.avif?t=1754938007\" width=600 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ogre Pixel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2025</p>",
